{"tid":901582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優夜歸遭3醉漢糾纏　美腿遭劃傷濺血","createTime":"2018-11-14T06:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T09:14:17.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"baefbab746445e8af7e77d999e53468e682eecd3","tid":901582,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"看了真讓人心疼！<br />\n<br />\n無妄之災！曾獲DMM成人大獎「最優秀女優獎」的日本人氣AV女優大槻響(大槻ひびき)日前在推特上自爆在外吃完飯後返家途中，竟遇到3名醉漢糾纏，結果被他們丟來的酒瓶給劃傷小腿，一條白皙美腿上多了一條怵目驚心的血痕，讓粉絲們看了相當不捨。<br />\n<br />\n大槻響在推特貼文上PO出傷痕照以及3名醉漢特徵，表示已經報警，她也發文表示還好傷痕淺，保證將不會影響接下來的活動，請粉絲們放寬心，也非常感謝大家的關心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWNsHGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWNsHGC.png&h=2c2e64d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33de4ca64a5dc1a57edaab012f5ff4a5b0116911","tid":901582,"uid":44243,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"平時睇av都唔覺佢有咁多腳毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有腳毛仲好 j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aae0beefaf0e12d0e38ab72c25befe458474ab","tid":901582,"uid":179967,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"專登上網GOOGLE <br />\n樓主我屌你老母"},{"pid":"0760feaf765ff2e3a8a141dd3702db8893c4281d","tid":901582,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"33de